Shore Road, east side, between 97th and 99th Streets. Iu 1890 on the Robinson's mape of Eings County, the homes in this view were on the Estate of Henry Stanton. The Estate of A. W. Johnson was south of the Stanton Estate and west ot Shore Road. The house in the foreground is the original Stanton
